author: Inside Edition
description: Some people are hesitant to discuss their age. Not Chuck Goad. The Scottsdale, Arizona grandfather is eager to share. He tells KPHO most of the inquiries come while he's at the LA Fitness, where he works out three to four days per week. It's also where he's been working as a personal trainer for the past 14 years. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: 86-Year-Old From Arizona is Oldest Physical Trainer in the World

author: Inside Edition
description: A woman who almost died in a fiery car wreck met the man who saved her life. Mary McLoryd's car caught fire with the retired school teacher trapped inside. A passing motorist grabbed a fire extinguisher and rushed to the scene, pulling McLoryd to safety through the car's sunroof. McLoryd finally left the hospital after 41 days. Her daughter, Rashida, became her full-time caretaker. McLoryrd's hero, 23-year-old Nathan Felix, met her for the first time since the crash.
title: Woman Reunites With Man Who Saved Her Life in Fiery Car Crash
